items.name: CANCELLED
desc: the context menu must not be executed.
The next registered XContextMenuInterceptor should not be notified.

items.name: CONTINUE_MODIFIED
desc: the menu has been modified and the next registered XContextMenuInterceptor should be notified.

items.name: EXECUTE_MODIFIED
desc: the menu has been modified and should be executed without notifying the next registered XContextMenuInterceptor.

items.name: IGNORED
desc: the XContextMenuInterceptor has ignored the call.
The next registered XContextMenuInterceptor should be notified.
